I ordered the tenders and fries for my daughter and she ate it all and she never finishes her food. Amazing restaurant. I will definitely be back and cater with them. Employees are very friendly. Perfectly done falafel, great assortment of sauces served on the side, rice, salad, and a pita on top of all that  Even better than the food was chatting with Steve! He took the time to talk to my friend and I, and clearly showed his culinary knowledge and passion for food. Seriously, he could probably talk about hummus all day.
